mdRecord.dcterms:title: Group Portrait of Storer College Class of 1895, Harpers Ferry, W. Va.
mdRecord.dcterms:description: Graduates in front of building on Storer Campus. First Row: John Willson, R.H. Parker, W.A. Saunders, S.B. Ellis. Second Row: Daisy Nickens, A.L. Tollierer, Harriet Brown. Third Row: Charles Bell, N. Wiley, Pela Penick.
